site.name: designated site name
time: 24 hrs(hh:mm) of net set (or of zoop if no set)
lat: latitude in decimal degrees of net set (or of CTD/Zoop/YSI if no set)
lon: longitude in decimal degrees of net set (or of CTD/Zoop/YSI if no set)
crew: full names separated by commas
set.number: If multiple sets at one site, enter which set entered (NA if not multiple sets)
set.type: targeted or random (NA if no set)
min.searching: number of minutes spent searching for fish
site.dimpling: dimpling activity(0 = none,1 = 1 school,2 = >1 school,3 = big swath)
site.sliders: sliding activity(0 = none,1 = 1 school,2 = >1 school,3 = big swath)
site.poppers: popping activity(0 = none,1 = 1 school,2 = >1 school,3 = big swath)
set.dimpling: dimpling activity(0 = none,1 = 1-15,2 = >15, NA if no set)
set.sliders: sliding activity(0 = none,1 = 1-15,2 = >15, NA if no set)
set.poppers: popping activity(0 = none,1 = 1-15,2 = >15, NA if no set)
so.total: total sockeye in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
cu.total: total chum in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
he.total: total herring in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
co.total: total coho in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
pi.total: total pink in net (rounded to nearest 10,100, or 1000)
bycatch.num.1: number of bycatch species #1 in net(NA if none)
bycatch.num.2: number of bycatch species #2 in net(NA if none)
bycatch.num.3: number of bycatch species #3 in net(NA if none)
mort.num.1: number of mort species #1 in net(NA if none)
mort.num.2: number of mort species #2 in net(NA if none)
mort.num.3: number of mort species #3 in net(NA if none)
SO.stockID: Range of 7 digit codes (DS#####-DS##### or JS#####-JS#####)
CO.stockID: Range of 7 digit codes (DC#####-DC##### or JC#####-JC#####)
HE.stockID: Range of 7 digit codes (DH#####-DH##### or JH#####-JH#####)
preserved: 1 = preserved correctly0 = not correctlyTBD = in dewarNA = no fish taken
